name: Frozen - Elsa
description:
If you like the LoRA, please feel free to share your generated images here and leave a review (or at least a rating) for the sake of motivation and stuff ;D

For usage guidance and trigger words description, look into the About this version box for more information and click on Show more.

Please contact me here on civitAi or on Twitter if you want to provide the LoRa in a generation service.

About

Well, I said I wouldn't create a LoRA for her, but I already had half of the data due to the Anna LoRa and someon I know requested it... So here it is, with I think all costumes (expect the stuff from wreck it ralph and lego) she wears. But my opinion is still Anna > Elsa.

While generating the examples I found out that some of the costumes are really hard to generate (or generate at all), so I will create an update soon to make it more easy use.

Training

A bit more data than I had for Anna, so we use 152 images for training.
